---
import Button from '@/components/ui/Button.astro';
---
  <section
    id="story"
    class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-16 bg-cream px-5 py-20 md:gap-24 md:px-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-[100px] lg:px-20 lg:py-[110px]"
  >
    <div class="story-image relative">
      <div class="story-img-main relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--cream)_72%,var(--gray-orange)_28%)]">
      </div>
      <div
        class="story-img-float absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 hidden aspect-square w-[55%] overflow-hidden bg-dark-red md:block"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -left-5 top-7 bg-dark-red px-5 py-3 font-display text-[11px] tracking-[0.3em] text-cream uppercase"
      >
        Est. 2015 · Pune
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-text">
      <div
        class="section-eyebrow mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.35em] text-gray-orange uppercase"
      >
        Our Story
      </div>
      <h2 class="mb-8 font-serif text-[clamp(30px,3.5vw,46px)] font-light leading-tight text-dark-brown">
        Born from a <em class="italic text-dark-red">Passion</em><br />for the Perfect Feast
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-5 font-body text-lg leading-[1.9] text-[var(--text-muted-on-cream)]">
        Elamrit began with a simple but profound belief: that every meal served at a meaningful occasion deserves the
        same reverence as the occasion itself. Founded in Pune by a team of culinary artisans and event specialists, we
        started with a singular focus — to make luxury catering accessible to those who appreciate the extraordinary.
      </p>
      <blockquote
        class="my-9 border-l-[3px] border-dark-red bg-light-blush py-4 pr-7 pl-7"
      >
        <p class="m-0 font-serif text-[19px] italic leading-relaxed text-dark-brown">
          "Elamrit crafts unforgettable culinary experiences, blending the richness of tradition with modern elegance."
        </p>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mb-5 font-body text-lg leading-[1.9] text-[var(--text-muted-on-cream)]">
        Over the years, our footprint has grown from intimate Pune celebrations to grand Pan India events — destination
        weddings in Rajasthan, corporate galas in Mumbai, anniversary feasts in Bangalore. Every event we touch carries
        the same DNA: meticulous preparation, seasonal ingredients, and service that anticipates before it responds.
      </p>
      <Button href="#" variant="storyLink">Our Full Journey</Button>
    </div>
  </section>
